column2: SELECT m.id as v0_idx, m.ra AS v0_ra, m.dec AS v0_dec, n.objid as sdssm_objid, n.distance as sdssm_distance, p.ra AS sdssm_p_ra, p.dec AS sdssm_p_dec, s.specObjId as sdssm_s_specObjId, s.plate, s.fiberID, s.mjd, s.ra as sdssm_s_ra, s.dec as sdssm_s_dec, s.z as sdssm_s_z, s.zerr as sdssm_s_zerr, s.zwarning as sdssm_s_zwarning, s.class as sdssm_s_class, s.subClass as sdssm_s_subClass, dbo.fPhotoTypeN (p.type) as sdssm_p_type, p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z, w.cntr as sdssm_w_cntr, w.w1mpro, w.w2mpro, w.w3mpro, w.w4mpro, xm.match_dist as sdssm_w_matchdist, w.w1cc_map, w.w2cc_map, w.w3cc_map, w.w4cc_map, w.ph_qual_det1, w.ph_qual_det2, w.ph_qual_det3, w.ph_qual_det4 into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.MyRaDecPairs2 AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid = p.objid LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID LEFT JOIN wise_xmatch xm ON s.bestObjID = xm.sdss_objid LEFT JOIN wise_allsky w on xm.wise_cntr = w.cntr
